# Changelog

**NOTE**: This is the changelog for the **Python** package that provide output loaders for the main output files from the main `cfDNAlab` command line tool. The changelog for the CLI tool is found [here](https://github.com/BesenbacherLab/cfDNAlab/blob/main/CHANGELOG).

## py-cfDNAlab 0.1.0

 - Adds zarr loaders for the outputs of `cfdna midpoints` and `cfdna ends`.